{"tid":2364413,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"布斯韋利士拒戴口罩入鋪被趕","createTime":"2021-01-13T03:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-13T14:45:40.000Z","uid":41343,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b6ded5e1d0b734363945ff8a825d8ec0e21e597f","tid":2364413,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:31:45.000Z","msg":"荷李活影星布斯韋利士（Bruce Willis）日前被影到進入加州一間藥房時未有戴口罩，引來場內人士不滿，當店員要求他用頸上頸巾掩住口鼻時，他亦非常不滿，最終被店員趕走。為此布斯韋利士剛發出聲明道歉：「這是我判斷不當，每個人外出都要注意安全，一起繼續戴口罩。」立即認錯。<br />\n<br />\n在家居隔離期間，他大部份時間都與前妻狄美摩亞（Demi Moore）及他們的子女 Scout、Rumer與Tallulah同住，享受天倫樂。不過同時亦傳來他與現任太太Emma Heming婚姻出現危機，因為Emma未有同行，一直留在洛杉磯與兩個較細的子女一起。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210113/YC5MJGUMG5GE7D4XMZWAESPMP4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210113%2FYC5MJGUMG5GE7D4XMZWAESPMP4%2F&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvESC3g8rst4cc2NZsp7q1N1o%3D&h=5051bb64\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20210113%2FYC5MJGUMG5GE7D4XMZWAESPMP4%2F&h=90df2d6a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/20210113/YC5MJGUMG5GE7D4XMZWAESPMP4/</a>"},{"pid":"955c678720b070bb4caf81eccb4e934169fac623","tid":2364413,"uid":36894,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:45:15.000Z","msg":"他大部份時間都與前妻狄美摩亞（Demi Moore）及他們的子女 Scout、Rumer與Tallulah同住，享受天倫樂。不過同時亦傳來他與現任太太Emma Heming婚姻出現危機，因為Emma未有同行，一直留在洛杉磯與兩個較細的子女一起。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82936cb38c01f8e3947d01f9c6098f529edebb73","tid":2364413,"uid":41343,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"955c678720b070bb4caf81eccb4e934169fac623","tid":2364413,"uid":36894,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-13T03:45:15.000Z","msg":"他大部份時間都與前妻狄美摩亞（Demi Moore）及他們的子女 Scout、Rumer與Tallulah同住，享受天倫樂。不過同時亦傳來他與現任太太Emma Heming婚姻